{"tid":1772660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2019  Person of the year","createTime":"2019-12-06T21:56:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T00:41:03.000Z","uid":200672,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c8e89fd6e7194a5c3e3c3df53d47fbb0c715e959","tid":1772660,"uid":200672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T21:56:37.000Z","msg":"美國彭博商業周刊選出本年度全球50大最具影響力人物&ldquo;彭博50&rdquo;（Bloomberg 50），&ldquo;香港示威者，前線戰士&rdquo;（Hong Kong Protesters, the Frontline Fighters）榜上有名。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;彭博50&rdquo;排名榜是第三年發表，由該通訊社在全球的記者和編輯選出，上榜者來自五個不同範疇，包括商界、娛樂界、金融、政治和科技。<br />\n<br />\n在此同時，美國時代周刊2019年度風雲人物（Person of the Year）的網民心儀人物或群體上月起接受投票，香港示威者（The Hong Kong Protestors）截至香港時間5日晚獲89%支持。<br />\n<br />\n彭博商業周刊在網站介紹&ldquo;香港示威者，前線戰士&rdquo;時，配以身穿黑衣、戴着黃色頭盔、眼罩、面罩的勇武示威者相片（見圖）。報道形容，港人的抗爭已持續六個月，始於港府強推逃犯條例修訂，觸發市民對中國司法制度不透明的恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n報道形容，這場沒有領袖號召或策畫，全靠網上討論區動員的運動，開始時主要是和平集會及示威，最多人一次有200萬人參與。之後警方與示威者的武力不斷升級，警方發射了約一萬發的催淚彈，甚至實彈鎮壓，警暴問題亦備受批評；示威者起初只是以雨傘抵擋催淚彈，其後開始投擲汽油彈，並大規模破壞港鐵設施。<br />\n<br />\n雖然政府最終撤回條例，但示威者仍堅持尋求真普選等民主訴求。香港政府及北京高官在香港局勢升級之時，一直寸步不讓，持續的動蕩令香港經濟付上代價，政府預期將出現10年來首見衰退，GDP較2018年收縮1.3%。<br />\n<br />\n在政治上，在剛結束的區議會選舉中，泛民取得壓倒勝利，同時美國總統特朗普亦簽署《香港人權與民主法案》，表達對香港示威者的支持。<br />\n<br />\n封面中有10名&ldquo;full gear（全副裝備）&rdquo;的香港人，代表着一眾香港前線&ldquo;無名英雄&rdquo;，圖中的Rick覺得榮譽應歸所有港人，&ldquo;如果沒有所有香港人支持，運動沒可能維持這麼久&rdquo;。報道亦指港府無視衝突把香港國際金融中心的地位推向窘局，Rick是在職人士，坦言自己工作的行業影響非常嚴重，卻覺得這是一個調整，&ldquo;香港經濟近年好像打了類固醇，金鋪、藥房只做遊客生意本身已經有問題，調整後可能會出現多的小店，更加多元化，由失衡去返平衡&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n至於由網民投票選出的時代周刊年度風雲人物心儀人物或群體，從上月起接受投票以來，香港抗爭者作為一個群體一直得到90%上下的支持。網民投票結果本周揭曉，而由《時代》編輯選出的年度風雲人物誰屬，將於本月11日揭盅。<br />\n<br />\n供網民票選的57個候選人物或群體中，除了香港示威者，榜上有雙位數字支持的包括有主演《John Wick 3》的好萊塢男星Keanu Reeves，他與&ldquo;氣候示威者&rdquo;（The Climate Strikers）同獲20%支持，瑞典環保少女Greta Thunberg亦有17%<br />\n<br />\n香港抗爭者登彭博最具影響人物榜時代周刊風雲人物也成大熱 - <a href=\"http://rfi.my/50mN.W\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frfi.my%2F50mN.W&d=3i4OsSLc5DEqZvEdVyqrucg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=0eb83b44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rfi.my/50mN.W</a>"},{"pid":"e003e4241b1ff44eb64020371f6d734ad8af8696","tid":1772660,"uid":200672,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T21:56:58.000Z","msg":"我地暫時第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d70ae2b8a3a191f65237f6c79ce543811283f02","tid":1772660,"uid":200672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T21:57:39.000Z","msg":"究竟係邊個當初提名我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3737ee08141cc5a41eee33da099eb789603bd6cd","tid":1772660,"uid":200672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T22:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnWwZof.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnWwZof.gif&h=85fbc3ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzyrOgB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzyrOgB.jpg&h=f83247e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"926756e299c2b77014189390a2a52a2937073ddf","tid":1772660,"uid":289021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T22:03:53.000Z","msg":"正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6cdf1ace03b071ab666099e52121a07333c3e6","tid":1772660,"uid":200672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"926756e299c2b77014189390a2a52a2937073ddf","tid":1772660,"uid":289021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T22:03:53.000Z","msg":"正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T22:06:11.000Z","msg":"大家記得128出嚟呀<br />\n我地就嚟半年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eda975a96cae8ee7e71b4d0401bd36bb110be635","tid":1772660,"uid":200672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T22:06:28.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"f1dfbeb671be82fc99e14e17363cad0b23914640","tid":1772660,"uid":200672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T22:06:41.000Z","msg":"等其他人可以睇到"},{"pid":"f2112b4c10f227a77cecb9b31f6c54290712412c","tid":1772660,"uid":46737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T22:43:48.000Z","msg":"首先多謝攬炒之母林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大半年時間炒熱到全球各國同中國開波"},{"pid":"af0cf25fefe60d946dd53f93bd893b863172b253","tid":1772660,"uid":2612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:41:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQkE87V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQkE87V.jpg&h=ca6df116&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}